{"title":"春耕谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社管天地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等阳雀把口开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等燕子进屋来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社管天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕生产早安排。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（安岳安农公社余如喜）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报好比二月花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日东升满天霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员春耕笑哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲猛过长江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报好比二月花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三台和平公社罗良中）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕日子新事多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕日子新事多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁田姐姐笑呵呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道上行人来问路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"错把姑娘叫大哥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（星光）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一寸春光一担金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司号员，余大发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把铜号腰间挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上工下工他指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜号吹得嘀嘀?，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从春节一开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情突然起变化："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他吹响出工号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员早就把地下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他吹响收工号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员老是不回家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大发急得生了气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙向社员发了话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“往天都听我指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今为啥变了卦？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家一齐把话答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你看这是啥季节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一寸春光一担金。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（春牛、春苗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔原载四川日报〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}